{"article_id":"bIO9ZhlV7NYLyFcK","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President-elect Donald Trump has picked retired Marine Gen. James Mattis","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"to be his secretary of defense ,","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"tapping yet another outspoken ex-military leader","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"who butted heads with the Obama administration","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"to shape and carry out his national security strategy .","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"If confirmed ,","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"the highly decorated battlefield commander would be only the second retired general","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"to become defense secretary","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"- and would require a special waiver from Congress in the form of separate legislation .","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"\" I will not tell you","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"that one of our great , great generals -","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"don ' t let it outside of this room , \"","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"Trump teased a rally in Cincinnati Thursday night ,","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"playing up the drama .","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"\" We are going to appoint 'Mad Dog ' Mattis as our secretary of defense ...","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"but we are not announcing it until Monday ,","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"so don ' t tell anyone .","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"He ' s great . \"","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"`` They say","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"he ' s the closest thing to Gen. George Patton","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"that we have","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"and it ' s about time , ''","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"he added ,","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"referring to the impolitic and aggressive battlefield commander in World War II .","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"`` It ' s about time . \"","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"Hours earlier , Trump 's transition team had denied","depth":5},{"id":26,"text":"that he had settled on a defense secretary","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"despite a report in The Washington Post","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"that Mattis was the choice .","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"`` No decision has been made yet with regard to Secretary of Defense , ''","depth":5},{"id":30,"text":"spokesman Jason Miller tweeted at 4:40 p.m .","depth":5},{"id":31,"text":"Mattis , 66 ,","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"so nicknamed for his salty language and obsessive dedication to the military ,","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"was the top U.S. commander in Iraq and Afghanistan from 2010 to 2013 .","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"He had earlier co-authored a counterinsurgency strategy manual","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"credited with helping to halt some of the worst sectarian violence in Iraq before the U.S. military withdrawal in December 2011 .","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"But as head of the U.S. Central Command he also clashed with President Barack Obama 's National Security Council , particularly over Iran ,","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"which Mattis has called \" the single most enduring threat to stability and peace in the Middle East . ''","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"It 's a view","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"that aligns more closely with Trump and his pick for White House national security adviser , retired Lt. Gen. Michael Flynn ,","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"whom the Obama administration had removed as head of the Defense Intelligence Agency in 2014 .","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"Both Trump and Flynn have advocated pulling out of an agreement","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"reached with Iran last year","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"to curtail its nuclear weapons program in exchange for a lifting of economic sanctions and eventually removing the arms embargo .","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"Yet not all of Mattis ' views are so in sync with Trump and Flynn ,","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"who have made friendly gestures to Russian President Vladimir Putin .","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"Mattis has expressed deep wariness of Russia 's intentions ,","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"saying","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"it wants \" to break NATO apart . \"","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"During the campaign Mattis did not hold back in criticizing Trump and some of his rhetoric ,","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"including the president-elect 's comments","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"that NATO was obsolete","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"and that its members do n't pay their fair share .","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"\" Some of those allies have lost more troops per capita in Afghanistan","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"than we have , ' '","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"Mattis ,","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"who also served as NATO ' s supreme allied commander for transformation ,","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"told in July .","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"\" Some of them are spending 20 percent of their national budget on defense . \"","depth":6},{"id":59,"text":"View","depth":2},{"id":60,"text":"Trump announces his pick for General 'Mad Dog ' Mattis as defense secretary","depth":3},{"id":61,"text":"At a rally in Cincinnati on Thursday , President-elect Donald Trump announced","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"that he picked retired Marine Gen. James Mattis","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"to be his secretary of defense .","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"On Trump ' s call for a ban on Muslim immigrants , Mattis said","depth":9},{"id":65,"text":"that such talk prompts U.S. allies to think","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"\" we have lost faith in reason . \"","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"\" They think","depth":12},{"id":68,"text":"we ' ve completely lost it , ''","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"he said .","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"`` This kind of thing is causing us great damage right now ,","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"and it ' s sending shock waves through this international system . ''","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"The general has also espoused some views","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"that break with the majority of his fellow military leaders .","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"He has expressed reservations","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"about allowing women to serve in combat ,","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"telling the Marines ' Memorial Club in San Francisco","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"that `` the idea","depth":13},{"id":78,"text":"of putting women in there","depth":13},{"id":79,"text":"is not setting them up for success . ''","depth":12},{"id":80,"text":"He has also questioned","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"whether the U.S. nuclear arsenal needs to consist of submarines , bombers and land-based missiles .","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"`` Is it time","depth":13},{"id":83,"text":"to reduce the Triad to a Diad ,","depth":13},{"id":84,"text":"removing the land‐based missiles ? ''","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"he asked the Senate Armed Services Committee last year .","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"The pick was swiftly lauded by the GOP national security establishment .","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"`` He brings a clear-eyed view to the potential adversaries","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"our nation faces ,","depth":12},{"id":89,"text":"including Russia , ''","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"Tom Spoehr , director of the Center for National Defense at the conservative Heritage Foundation , said in a statement ,","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"calling the general `` an outstanding selection for this critically important position . ''","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"Mattis has key backers on Capitol Hill ,","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"including Sen. John McCain , the Arizona Republican","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"who chairs the Armed Services Committee ,","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"which would lead the confirmation process .","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"`` General Mattis is one of the finest military officers of his generation and an extraordinary leader","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"who inspires a rare and special admiration of his troops , ''","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"McCain said in a recent statement .","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"`` He is a forthright strategic thinker .","depth":12},{"id":100,"text":"His integrity is unshakable and unquestionable .","depth":12},{"id":101,"text":"And he has earned his knowledge and experience the old-fashioned way :","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"in the crucible of our nation 's defense and the service of heroes .","depth":12},{"id":103,"text":"\" General Mattis has a clear understanding of the many challenges","depth":12},{"id":104,"text":"facing the Department of Defense , the U.S. military and our national security , ''","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"McCain added .","depth":11},{"id":106,"text":"Since retiring from the Marine Corps ,","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"Mattis has served on the board of defense giant General Dynamics , as well as Theranos , a Silicon Valley biotech company","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"that came under scrutiny for its business practices","depth":12},{"id":109,"text":"-","depth":12},{"id":110,"text":"and which Mattis reportedly advocated on behalf of before the military","depth":11},{"id":111,"text":"despite agreeing not to .","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"He 's also a fellow at the Hoover Institution , a conservative think tank at Stanford University in Palo Alto , Calif. ,","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"and has done some private consulting .","depth":9},{"id":114,"text":"Mattis ' elevation to Trump 's Cabinet would make him a first among equals .","depth":7},{"id":115,"text":"Apart from the president , only the defense secretary has the legal authority","depth":9},{"id":116,"text":"to order the military into action .","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"And","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"while the decision","depth":12},{"id":119,"text":"to launch a nuclear attack","depth":12},{"id":120,"text":"rests solely with the commander-in-chief ,","depth":11},{"id":121,"text":"the procedures require secondary confirmation from the defense secretary ,","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"though he does not get a veto .","depth":11},{"id":123,"text":"View Photo gallery","depth":5},{"id":124,"text":"Politicians , moguls and even a few Democrats :","depth":8},{"id":125,"text":"Trump 's revolving door of post-election visitors","depth":8},{"id":126,"text":"Political observers have closely watched Donald Trump ' s every move","depth":11},{"id":127,"text":"as he goes about the massive task","depth":13},{"id":128,"text":"of filling the thousands of political appointee jobs ,","depth":13},{"id":129,"text":"with acute interest in the makeup of his Cabinet .","depth":12},{"id":130,"text":"Hundreds of people have called on Trump ' s Manhattan office , rural New Jersey getaway and Mar-a-Lago resort in Florida over the past two months ;","depth":11},{"id":131,"text":"here ' s a day-by-day look at some of the people","depth":12},{"id":132,"text":"who have visited","depth":13},{"id":133,"text":"since Trump was elected .","depth":13},{"id":134,"text":"But","depth":12},{"id":135,"text":"to get the job","depth":14},{"id":136,"text":"Mattis will need something highly unusual :","depth":14},{"id":137,"text":"a waiver .","depth":13},{"id":138,"text":"As a result , his selection is viewed by some as a major departure from tradition .","depth":11},{"id":139,"text":"Mattis is technically ineligible","depth":14},{"id":140,"text":"to be Defense secretary","depth":14},{"id":141,"text":"because the law requires retired military officers to be out of uniform for seven years","depth":15},{"id":142,"text":"before they can become the military 's civilian leader .","depth":15},{"id":143,"text":"That 's in an effort","depth":15},{"id":144,"text":"to ensure","depth":16},{"id":145,"text":"that civilian control of the armed forces , a bedrock of the American democratic tradition , remains inviolate .","depth":16},{"id":146,"text":"Unless Congress votes","depth":15},{"id":147,"text":"and the president signs an exception ,","depth":15},{"id":148,"text":"`` a person may not be appointed as secretary of defense within seven years after relief from active duty as a commissioned officer of a regular component of an armed force , ''","depth":14},{"id":149,"text":"the law says .","depth":13},{"id":150,"text":"`` It happened once , ''","depth":17},{"id":151,"text":"Harold Brown ,","depth":19},{"id":152,"text":"who was defense secretary under President Jimmy Carter from 1977 to 1981 ,","depth":19},{"id":153,"text":"told .","depth":18},{"id":154,"text":"`` And that was George Marshall , '' the Army 's legendary chief of staff in World War II ,","depth":18},{"id":155,"text":"who went to become both secretary of State and secretary of defense under President Harry Truman .","depth":18},{"id":156,"text":"`` Congress had to pass a separate law","depth":18},{"id":157,"text":"exempting him . ''","depth":18},{"id":158,"text":"In 1994 , President Bill Clinton picked retired Adm. Bobby Inman","depth":18},{"id":159,"text":"to be Defense secretary ,","depth":18},{"id":160,"text":"but he had been off of active duty for the required period","depth":18},{"id":161,"text":"and his nomination was ultimately withdrawn anyway .","depth":18},{"id":162,"text":"When Congress passed a waiver for Marshall in 1950 ,","depth":17},{"id":163,"text":"it made clear","depth":18},{"id":164,"text":"it did not want to set a precedent .","depth":18},{"id":165,"text":"`` It is hereby expressed as the intent of the Congress","depth":17},{"id":166,"text":"that the authority","depth":19},{"id":167,"text":"granted by this Act","depth":19},{"id":168,"text":"is not to be construed as approval by the Congress of continuing appointments of military men to the office of Secretary of Defense in the future , ''","depth":18},{"id":169,"text":"its report","depth":18},{"id":170,"text":"accompanying the legislation","depth":18},{"id":171,"text":"said .","depth":17},{"id":172,"text":"`` It is hereby expressed as the sense of the Congress","depth":16},{"id":173,"text":"that","depth":17},{"id":174,"text":"after General Marshall leaves the office of secretary of defense ,","depth":18},{"id":175,"text":"no additional appointments of military men to that office shall be approved . ''","depth":18},{"id":176,"text":"Retired Marine Gen. James Mattis was the top U.S. commander in Iraq and Afghanistan from 2010 to 2013 .","depth":14},{"id":177,"text":"|","depth":15},{"id":178,"text":"AP Photo","depth":15},{"id":179,"text":"`` The Congress ' report at the time said","depth":17},{"id":180,"text":"it is very unusual , ''","depth":17},{"id":181,"text":"Brown said ,","depth":16},{"id":182,"text":"`` and should probably never happen again .","depth":15},{"id":183,"text":"This is a significant barrier ,","depth":16},{"id":184,"text":"though it is not an insuperable one .","depth":16},{"id":185,"text":"The Trump administration would have to make a very compelling case .","depth":16},{"id":186,"text":"Mattis does n't have the standing of George Marshall .","depth":17},{"id":187,"text":"They 'd have to make the case","depth":18},{"id":188,"text":"he is another George Marshall . ''","depth":18},{"id":189,"text":"Earlier this year , a bloc of GOP hawks","depth":15},{"id":190,"text":"who opposed Trump 's candidacy","depth":15},{"id":191,"text":"tried to persuade Mattis to run for president as a third-party candidate ,","depth":15},{"id":192,"text":"though he expressed no interest .","depth":15},{"id":193,"text":"Congressional aides say","depth":12},{"id":194,"text":"work is already underway","depth":13},{"id":195,"text":"to determine the legislative language","depth":14},{"id":196,"text":"needed to grant Mattis a waiver .","depth":14},{"id":197,"text":"Arnold Punaro , a former staff member of the Senate Armed Services Committee","depth":15},{"id":198,"text":"who helped craft the current statute ,","depth":15},{"id":199,"text":"said","depth":14},{"id":200,"text":"that","depth":15},{"id":201,"text":"while Mattis ' waiver would need to be approved by both houses of Congress","depth":16},{"id":202,"text":"and signed by the president ,","depth":16},{"id":203,"text":"he does not see it as a major problem .","depth":14},{"id":204,"text":"`` He would not in any way undermine or erode civilian control of the military ,","depth":14},{"id":205,"text":"and it would be hard to find someone","depth":16},{"id":206,"text":"who would be less likely to be pushed around by the military","depth":16},{"id":207,"text":"and he is now a civilian","depth":16},{"id":208,"text":"and would be firmly in charge , ''","depth":16},{"id":209,"text":"said Punaro ,","depth":14},{"id":210,"text":"calling Mattis a `` stellar choice . ''","depth":14},{"id":211,"text":"One of Mattis ' fellow retired generals also does n't anticipate","depth":13},{"id":212,"text":"it will pose much of a roadblock .","depth":13},{"id":213,"text":"`` Waivers are waivers , ''","depth":14},{"id":214,"text":"said retired Army Lt. Gen. Mick Bednarek ,","depth":15},{"id":215,"text":"who until last year was the top U.S. military adviser in Iraq .","depth":15},{"id":216,"text":"`` In the case of Jim Mattis , that would not be too contentious .","depth":14},{"id":217,"text":"The real issue is his views and perspectives . ''","depth":14},{"id":218,"text":"\" While I deeply respect General Mattis ' s service ,","depth":14},{"id":219,"text":"I will oppose a waiver , \"","depth":14},{"id":220,"text":"Sen. Kirsten Gillibrand of New York , a senior Democrat on the Armed Services Committee , \" said in a statement Thursday night .","depth":13},{"id":221,"text":"\" Civilian control of our military is a fundamental principle of American democracy ,","depth":13},{"id":222,"text":"and I will not vote for an exception to this rule . \"","depth":13},{"id":223,"text":"Others demanded","depth":11},{"id":224,"text":"that his views on torture and other human rights concerns be key to the Senate confirmation process .","depth":11},{"id":225,"text":"\" We have real concerns about human rights in a Trump Administration ,","depth":12},{"id":226,"text":"and we will demand","depth":13},{"id":227,"text":"that the Senate press General Mattis about his specific views and positions , \"","depth":13},{"id":228,"text":"Naureen Shah , director of Amnesty International USA ' s security with human rights program , said in a statement .","depth":11},{"id":229,"text":"Mattis is known as one of the most blunt battlefield commanders of his generation .","depth":7},{"id":230,"text":"He is mostly revered","depth":12},{"id":231,"text":"- but also reviled by some -","depth":12},{"id":232,"text":"for his rough edges and controversial comments , traits","depth":12},{"id":233,"text":"that have gotten him into hot water .","depth":12},{"id":234,"text":"\" You go into Afghanistan ,","depth":13},{"id":235,"text":"you got guys","depth":15},{"id":236,"text":"who slap around women for five years","depth":16},{"id":237,"text":"because they didn ' t wear a veil , \"","depth":16},{"id":238,"text":"he said in in 2005 .","depth":14},{"id":239,"text":"\" You know","depth":13},{"id":240,"text":"guys like that ain ' t got no manhood left anyway ,","depth":14},{"id":241,"text":"so it ' s a hell of a lot of fun to shoot them . \"","depth":14},{"id":242,"text":"Also in his rhetorical repertoire :","depth":12},{"id":243,"text":"\" The first time","depth":15},{"id":244,"text":"you blow someone away","depth":15},{"id":245,"text":"is not an insignificant event .","depth":14},{"id":246,"text":"That said ,","depth":15},{"id":247,"text":"there are some a -- -- -- -","depth":15},{"id":248,"text":"in the world","depth":15},{"id":249,"text":"that just need to be shot . \"","depth":15},{"id":250,"text":"But","depth":11},{"id":251,"text":"despite his candor ,","depth":12},{"id":252,"text":"Mattis is also considered a \" warrior monk '' for the library of books","depth":13},{"id":253,"text":"he carried from post to post ,","depth":14},{"id":254,"text":"ranging from Roman philosophy to Sun Tzu 's `` The Art of War . '' \" You are part of the world ' s most feared and trusted force , ''","depth":16},{"id":255,"text":"he once told forces under his command .","depth":16},{"id":256,"text":"`` Engage your brain","depth":16},{"id":257,"text":"before you engage your weapon . \"","depth":16},{"id":258,"text":"Mattis ,","depth":12},{"id":259,"text":"who is unmarried ,","depth":12},{"id":260,"text":"was also known as the rare commander","depth":13},{"id":261,"text":"who could be found visiting his troops in their fighting positions ,","depth":14},{"id":262,"text":"or volunteering to be the watch officer on Christmas","depth":15},{"id":263,"text":"so one of his underlings could be with his family .","depth":15},{"id":264,"text":"`` His dedication is unparalleled .","depth":14},{"id":265,"text":"He is married to the the nation , ''","depth":15},{"id":266,"text":"Bednarek told .","depth":15},{"id":267,"text":"`` He has a 100 percent focus on mission accomplishment .","depth":14},{"id":268,"text":"His forte is his leadership and his thoughtfulness . ''","depth":14},{"id":269,"text":"Retired Adm. William Fallon ,","depth":12},{"id":270,"text":"who was Mattis ' boss early in the Iraq War ,","depth":12},{"id":271,"text":"said","depth":11},{"id":272,"text":"he believes","depth":11},{"id":273,"text":"Mattis may be just the right person","depth":12},{"id":274,"text":"to run the Pentagon .","depth":12},{"id":275,"text":"While he has vast experience in war ,","depth":11},{"id":276,"text":"he has also been outspoken in recent years about the need for clearer goals and policies","depth":12},{"id":277,"text":"to guide it .","depth":12},{"id":278,"text":"`` The most important thing is that Jim 's got a really good understanding","depth":13},{"id":279,"text":"that you need to have a good policy framework","depth":14},{"id":280,"text":"before digging foxholes , ''","depth":14},{"id":281,"text":"Fallon told .","depth":12},{"id":282,"text":"`` He has been urging leadership to focus on coming up with policies","depth":13},{"id":283,"text":"before sending troops into action . ''","depth":13},{"id":284,"text":"`` That is what is really needed right now , ''","depth":13},{"id":285,"text":"Fallon added .","depth":13}],"relations":[{"parent":571,"left":344,"right":570,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":344,"left":310,"right":343,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":310,"left":294,"right":309,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":294,"left":290,"right":293,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":290,"left":287,"right":289,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":287,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":289,"left":2,"right":288,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":288,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":293,"left":292,"right":8,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":292,"left":5,"right":291,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":291,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":309,"left":298,"right":308,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":298,"left":296,"right":297,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":296,"left":295,"right":11,"relation":"restatement","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":295,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":297,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":308,"left":301,"right":307,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":301,"left":300,"right":17,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":300,"left":14,"right":299,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":299,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":307,"left":306,"right":24,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":306,"left":305,"right":23,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":305,"left":304,"right":22,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":304,"left":303,"right":21,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":303,"left":18,"rig